Dreckos are nonhostile critters that graze on <link=\"SPICEVINE\">Pincha Pepperplants</link>, <link=\"SWAMPLILY\">Balm Lily</link> or <link=\"BASICSINGLEHARVESTPLANT\">Mealwood Plants</link>.\n\nTheir backsides are covered in thick woolly fibers that only grow in <link=\"HYDROGEN\">Hydrogen</link> climates.